{"tid":691621,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"暴龍化石ifc免費睇","createTime":"2018-06-06T02:24:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-06T03:16:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"792cdcd6d4bf7efe7a64386ff127c01c1f21f6f4","tid":691621,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T02:24:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180606/20412294\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180606%2F20412294&d=kEmSxAroJEq%2Bdf0fzaYk5cPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=4392943d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180606%2F20412294&h=1964f1c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180606/20412294</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月06日 <br />\n<br />\n暴龍化石ifc免費睇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180606/large/a1003a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180606%2Flarge%2Fa1003a.gif&h=a0ca0201&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【首度曝光】■ifc明日起展出美洲暴龍TAD的化石。受訪機構提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】你對恐龍這種史前生物的認識有幾多？ifc商場於明日至27日舉行免費的「MEET THE T.REX︰探索暴龍世界」展覽，首次展出從未公開曝光的「美洲暴龍TAD」暴龍化石。展覽亦設有互動屏幕，模擬暴龍的頭髮及AR擴增實境模擬身體結構，呈現暴龍真實一面，讓公眾探索恐龍奧秘。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180606/large/a1003b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180606%2Flarge%2Fa1003b.gif&h=2e4505e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n參觀者可摸大腿骨<br />\n<br />\n來自美國西北部南達科他州Hardy County的暴龍化石，名為The American Dragon，簡稱TAD，尺寸長12米、高4米，重兩噸，於2014年完成發掘及組裝。全體超過三分之一為真正骨骼，比率極重，極為珍稀，其餘部份則由不易燃聚氨酯泡沫和鋼架或支架組成。<br />\n<br />\n該化石為一名考古學家及收藏家所擁有，原定於歐洲的博物館長期展出。主辦的領賢慈善基金主席張王幼倫表示，本想向英國大自然博物館借恐龍化石，但由於該化石正在巡迴展覽，因此造就了她借到更為珍貴的「美洲暴龍TAD」化石，用了近一年時間籌備，由申請展覽、運送程序及場地組裝等，牽涉到多個不同範疇的專業團隊。<br />\n<br />\nifc展覽還有清晰顯示暴龍牙洞的埃德蒙頓龍脊椎、長近9吋的暴龍牙齒等，參觀者可觸摸6,500萬年前的暴龍大腿骨，及顯示恐龍被消滅時間的白堊紀古近紀界線沉積物切片。<br />\n<br />\n■記者張文鈴  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n房署嘆慢板　加防鼠擋板要半年<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n奇女子案　內地人︰小題大做"},{"pid":"2455870b09e0faa0425e2517d13f6bccca876bfb","tid":691621,"uid":20379,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T02:26:20.000Z","msg":"賴有為"},{"pid":"379f0f4b60f843077ba31ce622d8e33e8787b7bc","tid":691621,"uid":55597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T02:30:34.000Z","msg":"暴龍的頭髮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"939acf9299ac56298e49d05a322b8f3a73ad6b91","tid":691621,"uid":182315,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T02:30:48.000Z","msg":"大腿骨應該會俾蝗蟲刻字"},{"pid":"7cc15acf655fea9f8f2d07cc5505074304b05454","tid":691621,"uid":33868,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T02:31:49.000Z","msg":"Jurassic World宣傳？"},{"pid":"b1862f967fea4767549892e2eb6ecea73b9781d0","tid":691621,"uid":65990,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T02:32:24.000Z","msg":"嗰隻專食細路仔好無人性喎"},{"pid":"2b3a5346fc87e1e285a32e3925279ff6b04fc73a","tid":691621,"uid":156363,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T02:35:23.000Z","msg":"恐龍頭骨終於搵翻，好野啊阿柒。"},{"pid":"8916d5cafafb63d64c96d6363adc8a056c49d5aa","tid":691621,"uid":55533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b1862f967fea4767549892e2eb6ecea73b9781d0","tid":691621,"uid":65990,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T02:32:24.000Z","msg":"嗰隻專食細路仔好無人性喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T02:37:48.000Z","msg":"白必圖一個轉身一射入波"},{"pid":"430e6edbff944bfbf155d763f57b66af21ae7e7b","tid":691621,"uid":19990,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"b1862f967fea4767549892e2eb6ecea73b9781d0","tid":691621,"uid":65990,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"c